summary: This is an email forwarding a Daily Beast article reporting the death of a victim who testified against Ghislaine Maxwell. The article was published on October 17, 2023, and notes the victim died in May of that year, with her family seeking answers.

persons.name: Ghislaine Maxwell
persons.context: She is the person against whom the deceased victim testified at trial.

events.title: Death of Epstein Victim
events.description: An Epstein victim who testified against Ghislaine Maxwell has died.

events.title: Ghislaine Maxwell's Trial
events.description: The deceased victim testified at the trial of Ghislaine Maxwell.

keyFacts: An Epstein victim who testified against Ghislaine Maxwell has died.
The victim's death occurred in May 2023.
The victim's family is seeking answers regarding her death.
The information is reported in a Daily Beast article from October 17, 2023.
